You asked we listened!! And hence we bring to you a complete new experience with new design and many mind blowing features to enhance your creativity.. New Features include: Brushes: Added a complete new set of brushes segregated in various categories like: Calligraphy Texture Floral Water Colour and many more Charms: Added new charms for Christmas and a few more Doodles: We have made an addition in our existing doodles. Stickers: Take a look at our new stickers to light up your festive greetings Shapes: You can now use shapes without any hassle I have worked really hard towards bringing this update and meeting your expectations. Feel free to share your reviews.
